	"Reverse Tracks can be unlocked by either going through story mode cups or through usage of the cheat menu. I had already used the cheat menu in my first tas of Hot Wheels so i believe there should be no problem to unlock the Reverse Tracks this way, it saves me so much time.
	$LF
