[h4 id=WhatChangedDuringMy1stSubmissionAnd11thSubmission 
	"What changed during my 1st submission and 11th submission
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"To be honest nothing really changed. I still tas the game the same way i did nearly 3 years ago. You would think to see a major improvement in tasing but that wasnt the case, aside from small rng improvement and better use of Ram Watch.
	$LF
